Meray dil ki dardkan kehti ha.
YA Allah jj Muhammad par slamti o barkat Nazil farma.
Tera mehboob mera b mehboob kab bna maloom nhi hua Ya Allah jj teri lela meri b lela ho gia maloom nhi hua kab 
Meray halay dil rehm farmya sakoon nhi yeh dil un say mulaqat ko baytab ha.
Hay marzay Muhammad dil ko lag gia deed hi dwa ha rehm farma.
Beshak yeh Muhhabat kay Alfaz hain mgr haqeqat main deed ho gi qiyamat walay din InshaAllah InshaAllah InshaAllah.
